-- Countrywide secures $12 bln in borrowing capacity
-- 
-- Thu Sep 13, 2007 9:40am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/09/13/us-countrywide-borrowing-idUSWNAS400120070913

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Countrywide Financial Corp CFC.N said on Thursday it recently arranged for $12 billion in additional secured borrowing capacity. 

 The No. 1 U.S. mortgage lender said the additional borrowing capacity came through new or existing credit lines. (Reporting by  Tim McLaughlin )